videos.headline: LSU WR catches short pass then maneuvers way to end zone
videos.description: LSU WR Ja'Marr Chase catches the pass, shakes a few defenders and then dives into the end zone.

videos.headline: LSU QB keeps it and scores from a yard out
videos.description: LSU QB Joe Burrow keeps it and walks into the end zone for his first LSU TD.

videos.headline: LSU WR leaps and grabs 40-yard TD right before the half
videos.description: LSU WR Stephen Sullivan out jumps multiple defenders and hauls in the 40-yard TD as the half ends.

videos.headline: LSU scoops up fumble and returns it 64 yards
videos.description: LSU safety JaCoby Evans returns fumble 64 yards down to the SELa 18-yard line.
